sense.def:
One's predecessor
je oseba, ki je opravljala neko delo ali imela neko vlogo pred osebo, o kateri govorimo.

seg.quote: She wasn't being paid the same wage as her predecessor.

sense.def:
The predecessor of an object or machine
je predmet ali stroj, ki ga je zamenjal predmet ali stroj, o katerem govorimo.

seg.quote: The latest model is more refined than its predecessor.
